Final is used to apply restrictions on class, method and variable. 
final class can't be inherited,  we can¡¯t extend that class or that class can¡¯t be extended 
we can¡¯t make subclass of that class.

final method can't be overridden
final variable value can't be changed.

Finally is used to place important code
it will be executed whether exception is handled or not.
The finally keyword is used in association with a try/catch block and guarantees that a section of code will be executed, 
even if an exception is thrown.